$BR 
$BR 
(a) \( f(p) = (p+$a1) \text{ mod } 26 \) 
\{ ans_rule(20) \}
$PAR
(b) \( f(p) = (p+$a2) \text{ mod } 26 \) 
\{ ans_rule(20) \}
$PAR
